complexity.name: Cyclomatic
complexity.description: A quantitative metric used to calculate the number of paths through the code.

cognitive_complexity.name: Cognitive
cognitive_complexity.description: A qualification of how hard it is to understand the code's control flow.

ncloc.name: Loc
ncloc.description: The number of physical lines that contain at least one character.

instability.name: Instability
instability.description: The relative susceptibility to breaking changes.

new_coverage.name: Coverage
new_coverage.description: A mix of line coverage and condition coverage on new lines.
